          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 975,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_014AxD6wGxkqKxsGFeMgVz9F\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"# Audience Summary\\n\\n**Primary Demographic:** Men in their 50s\\n\\n**Key Characteristics & Pain Points:**\\n- Have been told they're too old to get fit (facing age-related discouragement and limiting beliefs)\\n- Many have no prior fitness experience\\n- Struggling with the difficulty of starting a fitness journey after a lifetime of inactivity\\n\\n**Implied Needs:**\\n- Reassurance that fitness is achievable at their age\\n- Beginner-friendly approach that doesn't assume prior knowledge\\n- Overcoming psychological barriers and self-doubt about their ability to change\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":260,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":129,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
