          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1023,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01KGtbjNUhcdBCt11FnDaXRV\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"# Audience Summary\\n\\n**Primary Audience:** Men in their 50s\\n\\n**Key Insight:** This is an underserved market segment. The user has identified a gap in the fitness industry—there is currently insufficient catering to the specific needs of men in this age group.\\n\\n**User's Positioning:** The user is a fitness trainer with direct experience and expertise working with this demographic, positioning them well to address this unmet need.\\n\\n**Marketing Angle:** This audience represents an opportunity to fill a market void with specialized, age-appropriate fitness training tailored specifically for men aged 50+.\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":295,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":129,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
