          "bodySize": 1123,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1123,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_019QS5LDmHu3wwb3L9qNKQcM\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"# Business Idea Summary\\n\\n**Core Concept:** A fitness training business specializing in men in their 50s\\n\\n**Key Details:**\\n- **Industry:** Fitness/Personal Training\\n- **Founder Background:** Experienced fitness trainer\\n- **Target Market:** Men in their 50s\\n- **Market Gap:** Currently underserved demographic—no existing businesses adequately cater to this age group\\n- **Unique Positioning:** Specialized focus on the specific fitness needs, goals, and considerations of men in their 50s\\n\\n**Implied Value Proposition:** Tailored fitness training designed specifically for the 50+ male demographic, addressing their unique physical requirements and fitness goals that mainstream fitness services overlook.\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":311,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":154,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
