            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1370,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_019vZERJgBkbhGv4fPp7CEuv\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"# Summary\\n\\nI don't have enough information to provide a complete summary of the business idea. The chat history only shows a single assistant message asking about the audience, but it doesn't include:\\n\\n- The user's response to this question\\n- Previous messages describing the actual business idea\\n- Details about the product/service\\n- The problem being solved\\n- Target market information\\n- Any other context from earlier in the conversation\\n\\n**To create an effective summary for marketing copy, I would need:**\\n\\n1. The user's answer about their audience\\n2. Earlier conversation messages that outline the core business idea\\n3. Any details about unique value propositions, features, or differentiators\\n4. Information about the problem/opportunity the business addresses\\n\\nCould you provide the complete chat history or the user's response to the audience question? That will allow me to capture all the details needed for persuasive marketing copy.\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":147,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":190,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
